author: timesofindia.indiatimes.com
title: Brucelee's Leh Chalo becomes a viral hit online
text: Bruce Lee The Fighter, Ram Charan's upcoming mega release, starring Rakul Preet, Kriti Kharbanda with Mega Star Chiranjeevi in a special cameo, and directed by Srinu Vaitla with producer DVV Danayya under DVV Entertainments, recently released their first song, "Leh Chalo" on the official DVV Entertainments channel. The song (music by Thaman) has become a viral hit with over 1.2 lakh views within a few hours of its release. The recently released teaser of the film was also a huge hit among audiences with nearly 1.5 million views. The film is slated for a Dasara release on the 16th of October and the audio launch is scheduled on the 2nd of October.
